    "v3": "Yet not to them is giv&#39;n The mighty truth to know, To lift the fleshly veil which hides Incarnate God below.",
    "v4": "The secret of the Lord Escapes each human eye, And faithful pond&#39;ring hearts await The full epiphany.",
    "v5": "Lord, visit Thou our souls, And teach us by Thy grace Each dim revealing of Thyself With loving awe to trace;"
  },
